short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save a list of all the tabs you currently have open in your window so you can open them later.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save a list of all the tabs you currently have open so you can use them again later. Tabs saved here are kept in a list of tab groups referred to as 'Sessions' and can be opened up in the exact same order even after the browser had been quit and or the computer powered down.
